article_title: Aetna's On A Roll Ahead Of Humana Deal

article_metadata.description: Buoyed by new government business, Aetna (AET) once again raised its profit forecasts as the health insurer works through a proposed $37 billion acquisition of Humana (HUM) that will make the company an even larger player in expanding business under the Affordable Care Act.
